txt.en: 'I am surprised the Orcs have not eaten me yet!'
Captured soldiers are being held by the Enemy in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should free any captured soldiers that you find.
'I had thought this was the end of me.'

'A group of soldiers was recently ambushed in Parth Daenath, but they were not slain. No, they were taken prisoner instead. Some were taken to the Orc encampment of Mokh Darga, and the others were taken to the fortress of Amon Fuin. I know not why, but their capture must be for the purpose of gaining information. Even were that not so, we must try to bring them back from darkness. We cannot leave them to this torment.'
Celeborn can be found at Echad-in-Edhil.\n\nYou should talk to Celeborn.

'All of the captured soldiers were rescued and brought safely back to Adambel? You have done well indeed, bringing joy to my heart and dealing a blow to the efforts of the Dark Lord. He will learn nothing of our plans, not on this day.'
Celeborn has learned that a group of soldiers was recently captured by the Enemy.
